释义：
What... like? ……怎么样？
What's ... like?与 How ... 具有相同的含义。经常会与 What does ... look like?作比较，What ... like?表示人物（事物）的性格（性质），而 What does ... look like?单纯表示外观（appearance）。
例句：
What is your girlfriend like?
你女朋友怎么样？
What is the weather like in New York?
纽约的天气怎么样？
What was the show like last night?
昨晚的演出怎么样？
对话：
A: What is the new department store like?
新百货商场怎么样？
B: Awesome! It has a lot of brand-name products.
棒极了！有很多全新的商品。